  <trk>
    <name>W28 Gstaad - Eggli - Saanen - Gstaad</name>
    <desc><![CDATA[Enjoyable hike for beginners and connoisseurs up to the pleasure and local mountain of Gstaad. When the cable car is open, altitude meters can be saved and above all a fine meal can be enjoyed in the Eggli Lounge. A stopover is worthwhile. The descent is leisurely and offers great views over the ridge to Saanen. And from there back to Gstaad. / Please observe the operating times of the cable car! / Live info]]></desc>
    <type>hikingTourTrail</type>
